data.description: Exclusive Lucent Townhome Style condominium in Civita! One of only 5 units in the coveted Lucent community with spectacular views from every floor! The only unit with complete privacy in front and behind. Nestled on a canyon ridge overlooking all of Mission Valley with 180 degree panoramic sight lines. See 4 sets of fireworks all at once! Four stories, 3 bedrooms, all en suite with own baths, with stunning impeccable designer upgrades throughout. See supplement for complete list.Highly upgraded unique 4 story condominium with designer upgrades, accents, and fixtures. Glass subway tile backsplash in kitchen with real wood shaker style espresso cabinets. Kitchen also boasts rollout pantry shelving, and Restoration Hardware 18" Clemson Pendants in Bronze over kitchen island. Family Room/Great Room has surround sound and is pre-wired for plasma tv mounts in all rooms. Summit Brick wall has been added to second and third floors making it like a NYC loft! Modern and contemporary. Monarch maple wood stained posts and steel stair rails with added stair lighting for evening illuminated footpath. European White Oak Wood floors throughout and on stairs with upgraded porcelain tile everywhere else. UV custom solar powered motorized window shades in every room. Two balconies on the second floor making the cross breeze cool and fresh without your HVAC being needed most of the year. Entire home professionally painted with Dunn Edwards paint. Custom closets in both masters. Minka 58" lucite ceiling fans with LED lighting on 3rd and 4th floors. Appliances are high end. Samsung washer and steam dryer and a tankless water heater.
